{
  "texts": [
    "Recently, however, Sharma and colleagues have begun to compare the unique contribution of different dimensions within reappraisal, showing, for example, that people prefer reappraisals that are also very empathic (Sharma, Rushton, Lin, Wadden, et al., 2023).",
    "Finally, a recent paper examined whether LLMs can be used to help people improve their reappraisals to others (Sharma, Rushton, Lin, Nguyen, et al., 2023).",
    "These projects provide initial evidence that AI-assisted reappraisal functions are viable in emotional support.",
    "The field of AI and emotional support is burgeoning, but little of it is focused on comparing human and AI.",
    "Two recent exceptions are especially noteworthy."
  ]
}